						<p><hi rend="bold">King: ⎯⎯ Year: ⎯⎯</hi></p>						

						<p>A warrior is portrayed holding a bow while an animal (tiger) is facing him. It is damaged. Records the death of a certain Mahāvalli, in a tiger hunt, probably at Maṅgalapuram.</p>						

						<p>This inscription on the grounds of palaeography may be assigned to the 13th century A.D.</p>						

						</summary>
